### Accommodation HTTP tests for AccommodationServiceImpl via AccommodationController

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accommodationId = 2
@hostId = 2

### Create a new accommodation
POST {{baseUrl}}/accommodations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "host": {
    "id": {{hostId}}
  },
  "title": "Apartamento en Los laureles del Sur",
